@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### CADASTRO: sucesso
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "email": "",
  "password": "",
  "level": ""
}


### CADASTRO: falha -> email já cadastrado
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "outro_username",
  "email": "teste@lyricsflow.com",
  "password": "OutraSenha123",
  "level": "ADVANCED"
}


### LOGIN
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste@lyricsflow.com",
  "password": "OutraSenha123"
}


### LISTA MÚSICA
GET {{baseUrl}}/song
Accept: application/json


### INICIAR TAREFA (Endpoint /start)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 3,
    "songId": 1,
    "profile": {
        "languageLevel": "INTERMEDIATE"
    }
}


### TAREFA: Enviar resposta
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/3/submit
Content-Type: application/json

    [
        "shine",
        "meanwhile", 
        "presence", 
        "blessings", 
        "biased", 
        "significant", 
        "bars", 
        "complete", 
        "grateful", 
        "existence", 
        "Faithful"
    ]


### FLASHCARDS: Listar todos os flashcards de um usuário
GET {{baseUrl}}/flashcards?userId=3
Accept: application/json


### FLASHCARDS: Revisar um Flashcard isolado via pesquisa direta
POST {{baseUrl}}/flashcards/review-search?userId=3&word=bars&quality=MEDIUM
Content-Type: application/json


### FLAHSCARDS: revisão espaçada
GET {{baseUrl}}/flashcards/next?userId=3
Accept: application/json


### FLASHCARDS: Responder flahscard
POST {{baseUrl}}/flashcards/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flashcardId": 7,
  "quality": "EASY"
}

### MÚSICA: Testar busca e persistência na nova estrutura
POST {{baseUrl}}/song/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "All that matters",
  "artist": "Justin Bieber"
}

### TAREFA: Gerar tarefa usando o ID da música que acabou de ser salva
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 2,
    "songId": 39
}
